{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"tool_OuB7YaruBTw8K1OVGMhUrUGM","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"instcopilot-api product API tool\"\n\nSearch results for query: instcopilot-api product API tool instcopilot-api documentation instcopilot-api features\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"InstCopilot API\",\"url\":\"https://lmspeed.net/provider/instcopilot-api-com/health\"},{\"title\":\"GitHub - ericc-ch/copilot-api: Turn GitHub Copilot into OpenAI/Anthropic API compatible server. Usable with Claude Code!\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/ericc-ch/copilot-api\"},{\"title\":\"DuckCoding - Claude Code & CodeX & Gemini CLI 提供商\",\"url\":\"https://docs.duckcoding.ai/\"},{\"title\":\"Document API\",\"url\":\"https://docs.github.com/en/copilot/tutorials/customization-library/prompt-files/document-api\"},{\"title\":\"InstCopilot API - Claude Code 提供商\",\"url\":\"https://doc.instcopilot-api.com/\"},{\"title\":\"AI 助手集成嵌入指南 - 衡石分析平台\",\"url\":\"https://docs.hengshi.com/v5.3/copilot-sdk.html\"},{\"title\":\"Introducing API Copilot - Your AI-powered Integration Assistant | APIMatic Documentation\",\"url\":\"https://docs.apimatic.io/changelog/introducing-api-copilot/\"},{\"title\":\"AI编程工具：Claude Code安装和使用\",\"url\":\"https://aicoding.juejin.cn/post/7524880809565290506\"},{\"title\":\"API Reference | Copilot SDK - YourGPT\",\"url\":\"https://copilot-sdk.yourgpt.ai/docs/api-reference\"},{\"title\":\"API Documentation Strategy Using GitHub Copilot\",\"url\":\"https://hansem.com/blog/github-copilot-api-documentation-automation/\"},{\"title\":\"InSkill Launches Public Developer API to Accelerate Industrial ...\",\"url\":\"https://inskill.ai/press-release/inskill-launches-public-developer-api-to-accelerate-industrial-ai-copilot-integrations/\"},{\"title\":\"Extend your agent with tools from a REST API (preview)\",\"url\":\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-copilot-studio/agent-extend-action-rest-api\"}]\n\nHere are the search results for **\"instcopilot-api product API tool\"**:\n\n## Primary Result: InstCopilot API (Claude Code Provider)\n\n**InstCopilot API** appears to be a third-party API service specifically designed as a **Claude Code provider**, primarily targeting Chinese developers.\n\n- **Official Docs**: [doc.instcopilot-api.com](https://doc.instcopilot-api.com/)\n- **Console**: [instcopilot-api.com/console/token](https://instcopilot-api.com/console/token)\n- **Service Model**: Pay-as-you-go (\"按量计费\") with a focus on stability for Claude Code users\n\n### Key Features\n- **Claude Code Integration**: Dedicated API endpoints for Anthropic's Claude Code CLI tool\n- **Multiple Regions**: Provides endpoints such as:\n  - `https://jp.instcopilot-api.com` (Japan)\n  - `https://cn1.instcopilot-api.com` (China)\n- **Authentication**: Uses standard Anthropic-style API keys (`sk-xxx`) via:\n  - Environment variables: `ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN` and `ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL`\n  - Or `settings.json` configuration\n\n### Setup Configuration\nUsers configure Claude Code to point to InstCopilot's endpoints instead of Anthropic's official API:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"env\": {\n    \"ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN\": \"sk-your-instcopilot-key\",\n    \"ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL\": \"https://cn1.instcopilot-api.com\",\n    \"CLAUDE_CODE_MAX_OUTPUT_TOKENS\": \"32000\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### Platform Support\nThe documentation includes setup guides for:\n- **Windows** (PowerShell/CMD environment variables)\n- **macOS**\n- **Linux** (Ubuntu, CentOS, Debian, Arch)\n\n---\n\n## Related / Similar Products Found\n\n| Product | Description |\n|---------|-------------|\n| **ericc-ch/copilot-api** (GitHub) | Open-source tool that converts GitHub Copilot into an OpenAI/Anthropic-compatible API server |\n| **APIMatic API Copilot** | AI-powered integration assistant for generating SDK code and API documentation |\n| **Microsoft Copilot Studio** | Enterprise agent builder with REST API tool integration (OpenAPI spec support) |\n| **YourGPT Copilot SDK** | `@yourgpt/copilot-sdk` — SDK for building custom copilot/chat UIs |\n| **DuckCoding** | Another Claude Code provider that references InstCopilot API as a customer service contact |\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n**InstCopilot API** is essentially a **reseller/proxy API service** for Claude Code, offering regional endpoints and alternative billing/payment methods (likely more accessible in China). It is not a general-purpose \"API tool\" in the traditional sense, but rather a **specialized LLM API provider** optimized for AI coding workflows via Claude Code.\n\nWould you like me to search for more specific information about pricing, API compatibility, or alternatives to InstCopilot?\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1bce87ba-92dd-4044-a2ae-fdc31dc6849c","uuid":"0623c058-7e0d-4dc6-95d8-a7c9bc3443a3","timestamp":"2026-05-21T20:04:10.412Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"instcopilot-api product API tool","results":["Search results for query: instcopilot-api product API tool instcopilot-api documentation instcopilot-api features",{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_d87ma3omtdpc73f8gf70","content":[{"title":"InstCopilot API","url":"https://lmspeed.net/provider/instcopilot-api-com/health"},{"title":"GitHub - ericc-ch/copilot-api: Turn GitHub Copilot into OpenAI/Anthropic API compatible server. Usable with Claude Code!","url":"https://github.com/ericc-ch/copilot-api"},{"title":"DuckCoding - Claude Code & CodeX & Gemini CLI 提供商","url":"https://docs.duckcoding.ai/"},{"title":"Document API","url":"https://docs.github.com/en/copilot/tutorials/customization-library/prompt-files/document-api"},{"title":"InstCopilot API - Claude Code 提供商","url":"https://doc.instcopilot-api.com/"},{"title":"AI 助手集成嵌入指南 - 衡石分析平台","url":"https://docs.hengshi.com/v5.3/copilot-sdk.html"},{"title":"Introducing API Copilot - Your AI-powered Integration Assistant | APIMatic Documentation","url":"https://docs.apimatic.io/changelog/introducing-api-copilot/"},{"title":"AI编程工具：Claude Code安装和使用","url":"https://aicoding.juejin.cn/post/7524880809565290506"},{"title":"API Reference | Copilot SDK - YourGPT","url":"https://copilot-sdk.yourgpt.ai/docs/api-reference"},{"title":"API Documentation Strategy Using GitHub Copilot","url":"https://hansem.com/blog/github-copilot-api-documentation-automation/"},{"title":"InSkill Launches Public Developer API to Accelerate Industrial ...","url":"https://inskill.ai/press-release/inskill-launches-public-developer-api-to-accelerate-industrial-ai-copilot-integrations/"},{"title":"Extend your agent with tools from a REST API (preview)","url":"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-copilot-studio/agent-extend-action-rest-api"}]},"Here are the search results for **\"instcopilot-api product API tool\"**:\n\n## Primary Result: InstCopilot API (Claude Code Provider)\n\n**InstCopilot API** appears to be a third-party API service specifically designed as a **Claude Code provider**, primarily targeting Chinese developers.\n\n- **Official Docs**: [doc.instcopilot-api.com](https://doc.instcopilot-api.com/)\n- **Console**: [instcopilot-api.com/console/token](https://instcopilot-api.com/console/token)\n- **Service Model**: Pay-as-you-go (\"按量计费\") with a focus on stability for Claude Code users\n\n### Key Features\n- **Claude Code Integration**: Dedicated API endpoints for Anthropic's Claude Code CLI tool\n- **Multiple Regions**: Provides endpoints such as:\n  - `https://jp.instcopilot-api.com` (Japan)\n  - `https://cn1.instcopilot-api.com` (China)\n- **Authentication**: Uses standard Anthropic-style API keys (`sk-xxx`) via:\n  - Environment variables: `ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN` and `ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL`\n  - Or `settings.json` configuration\n\n### Setup Configuration\nUsers configure Claude Code to point to InstCopilot's endpoints instead of Anthropic's official API:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"env\": {\n    \"ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN\": \"sk-your-instcopilot-key\",\n    \"ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL\": \"https://cn1.instcopilot-api.com\",\n    \"CLAUDE_CODE_MAX_OUTPUT_TOKENS\": \"32000\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### Platform Support\nThe documentation includes setup guides for:\n- **Windows** (PowerShell/CMD environment variables)\n- **macOS**\n- **Linux** (Ubuntu, CentOS, Debian, Arch)\n\n---\n\n## Related / Similar Products Found\n\n| Product | Description |\n|---------|-------------|\n| **ericc-ch/copilot-api** (GitHub) | Open-source tool that converts GitHub Copilot into an OpenAI/Anthropic-compatible API server |\n| **APIMatic API Copilot** | AI-powered integration assistant for generating SDK code and API documentation |\n| **Microsoft Copilot Studio** | Enterprise agent builder with REST API tool integration (OpenAPI spec support) |\n| **YourGPT Copilot SDK** | `@yourgpt/copilot-sdk` — SDK for building custom copilot/chat UIs |\n| **DuckCoding** | Another Claude Code provider that references InstCopilot API as a customer service contact |\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n**InstCopilot API** is essentially a **reseller/proxy API service** for Claude Code, offering regional endpoints and alternative billing/payment methods (likely more accessible in China). It is not a general-purpose \"API tool\" in the traditional sense, but rather a **specialized LLM API provider** optimized for AI coding workflows via Claude Code.\n\nWould you like me to search for more specific information about pricing, API compatibility, or alternatives to InstCopilot?"],"durationSeconds":43.28623789499997,"searchCount":1}}
