{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"tool_jxHMgZ7PSMDzvKK9wpaO9JqA","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"\"instcopilot-api\" pricing Claude Code API provider documentation features\"\n\nSearch results for query: instcopilot-api pricing Claude Code API provider documentation instcopilot-api features\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"GitHub - danielalves96/claude-code-provider-gateway: The easiest way to use Claude Code with any LLM. Install the app, pick your provider, done.\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/danielalves96/claude-code-provider-gateway\"},{\"title\":\"Openai-Claude-Deepseek-API-provider/en.md at main\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/TechnologyStar/Openai-Claude-Deepseek-API-provider/blob/main/en.md\"},{\"title\":\"Microsoft AI Pricing Comparison: AI Builder vs API Call\",\"url\":\"https://www.linkedin.com/posts/suhail-powerflow_here-are-2-pricing-screenshots-essentially-activity-7427630044212273152--c-0\"},{\"title\":\"Claude Instant API Pricing 2026 - Costs, Performance & Providers\",\"url\":\"https://pricepertoken.com/pricing-page/model/anthropic-claude-instant\"},{\"title\":\"feat: Add Claude Code CLI as an AI Provider Option\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/eyaltoledano/claude-task-master/issues/705\"},{\"title\":\"Feature Request: Add Claude (Anthropic) as LLM Provider\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/icereed/paperless-gpt/issues/477\"},{\"title\":\"Support custom Claude provider model aliases\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/coleam00/Archon/issues/1586\"},{\"title\":\"Enable Prompt Caching for Claude Code Provider (Persistent Session Architecture) · cline/cline · Discussion #9892\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/cline/cline/discussions/9892\"},{\"title\":\"GitHub - ericc-ch/copilot-api: Turn GitHub Copilot into OpenAI/Anthropic API compatible server. Usable with Claude Code!\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/ericc-ch/copilot-api\"},{\"title\":\"Introducing web search on the Anthropic API\",\"url\":\"https://www.anthropic.com/news/web-search-api\"},{\"title\":\"Authentication - Claude Code Docs\",\"url\":\"https://code.claude.com/docs/en/authentication\"},{\"title\":\"ai-sdk-provider-claude-code/CHANGELOG.md at main · ben-vargas/ai-sdk-provider-claude-code\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/ben-vargas/ai-sdk-provider-claude-code/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md\"},{\"title\":\"Improvements in Claude Code Provider Integration\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/RooCodeInc/Roo-Code/issues/5060\"},{\"title\":\"Enable real-time token-by-token streaming for Claude Code provider\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/cline/cline/issues/6997\"},{\"title\":\"GitHub - cabinlab/litellm-claude-code: LiteLLM provider for Claude Code SDK - OpenAI-compatible API interface\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/cabinlab/litellm-claude-code\"}]\n\nLet me search more specifically for the **instcopilot-api.com** website to find their official pricing and features documentation. 搜索中: instcopilot-api.com pricing models API features documentation 搜索中...  我找到了一些 **inscopilot / instcopilot-api** 的相关信息。让我再进行一次更精确的搜索来获取详细的定价和功能信息。 搜索中: site:instcopilot-api.com OR \"instcopilot\" pricing API docs 搜索中... 很抱歉，直接访问 **instcopilot-api.com** 的详细定价页面似乎没有在搜索结果中显示具体内容。不过，根据现有搜索结果，我可以为您整理以下信息：\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 搜索结果摘要\n\n### 1. **instcopilot-api (inscopilot)** — 第三方 API 聚合平台\n\n根据 [GitHub 上的第三方 API 提供商列表](https://github.com/TechnologyStar/Openai-Claude-Deepseek-API-provider/blob/main/en.md) 显示：\n\n| 属性 | 详情 |\n|------|------|\n| **官网** | https://instcopilot-api.com |\n| **推荐度** | ⭐ 推荐 (recommended) |\n| **新用户奖励** | **$5 注册赠金** |\n| **特点** | 稳定、价格实惠 (stable and affordable) |\n| **支付方式** | 支持信用卡 (supports credit cards) |\n| **支持模型** | Claude、OpenAI、DeepSeek 等（作为 API 聚合商） |\n\n**注意**：这是一个**第三方 API 转发/聚合服务**，并非 Anthropic 官方 Claude API。\n\n---\n\n### 2. **Claude Code API 提供商生态** (相关工具与文档)\n\n如果您需要在 Claude Code 中使用不同的 API 提供商，以下是搜索中发现的相关开源工具：\n\n#### A. **claude-code-provider-gateway (CCPG)**\n- **作者**: danielalves96\n- **功能**: 为 Claude Code 提供\"控制层\"，支持切换不同 LLM 提供商\n- **支持提供商**: OpenRouter、OpenAI、Copilot、Ollama、本地模型等\n- **特点**: \n  - 本地运行，MIT 开源\n  - 无需 Node.js/npm，桌面应用一键安装\n  - 可按需切换便宜模型或强推理模型\n- **GitHub**: https://github.com/danielalves96/claude-code-provider-gateway\n\n#### B. **copilot-api** (by ericc-ch)\n- **功能**: 将 GitHub Copilot 转换为 OpenAI/Anthropic API 兼容服务器\n- **用途**: 可直接与 Claude Code 配合使用\n- **特点**: 支持速率限制控制 (`--rate-limit`, `--wait`)\n- **GitHub**: https://github.com/ericc-ch/copilot-api\n\n#### C. **litellm-claude-code**\n- **功能**: Docker 化的 LiteLLM + Claude Code SDK 提供方\n- **特点**: \n  - 使用 Claude Pro/Max OAuth 认证（无需 API Key）\n  - 提供 OpenAI 兼容 API 接口\n  - 支持所有 Claude 模型 (Opus, Sonnet, Haiku)\n- **GitHub**: https://github.com/cabinlab/litellm-claude-code\n\n---\n\n### 3. **官方 Claude Code 认证与文档**\n\n| 资源 | 链接 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **Claude Code 文档** | https://code.claude.com/docs | 官方文档首页 |\n| **认证方式** | https://code.claude.com/docs/en/authentication | 支持 Claude.ai 账户、Teams/Enterprise、Console、云服务商 (Bedrock/Vertex AI/Foundry) |\n| **Web Search API** | https://www.anthropic.com/news/web-search-api | Anthropic 官方 API 新增联网搜索功能，$10/千次搜索 + 标准 token 费用 |\n\n---\n\n### 4. **Claude 官方 API 定价参考** (对比用)\n\n根据 [pricepertoken.com](https://pricepertoken.com/pricing-page/model/anthropic-claude-instant)：\n- **Claude Instant**: $0.80 / 百万输入 tokens，$2.40 / 百万输出 tokens\n- **Web Search 功能**: $10 / 1000 次搜索（额外计费）\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ 重要提醒\n\n1. **instcopilot-api 是第三方聚合平台**，非 Anthropic 官方服务。使用第三方 API 提供商需注意：\n   - 数据隐私与安全风险\n   - 服务稳定性取决于转发商\n   - 可能违反某些服务条款（Anthropic 已于 2026 年 1 月开始阻止订阅版 OAuth Token 在官方 CLI 外使用）\n\n2. **Claude Code 官方支持**的认证方式包括：\n   - Claude Pro/Max 个人订阅\n   - Claude for Teams / Enterprise\n   - Claude Console (API Key 计费)\n   - 云平台: Amazon Bedrock、Google Vertex AI、Microsoft Foundry\n\n---\n\n如果您需要 **instcopilot-api.com** 的具体模型价格表（如 Claude 3.5 Sonnet、GPT-4o 等的 $/1M tokens 定价），建议直接访问其官网 https://instcopilot-api.com 查看，或联系其客服获取最新价目表，因为第三方聚合商的定价会随市场波动。\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1bce87ba-92dd-4044-a2ae-fdc31dc6849c","uuid":"a26e7b96-cda5-4727-8011-1497041b49c0","timestamp":"2026-05-21T20:06:00.283Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"\"instcopilot-api\" pricing Claude Code API provider documentation features","results":["Search results for query: instcopilot-api pricing Claude Code API provider documentation instcopilot-api features",{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_d87mav9arjis73f3pgj0","content":[{"title":"GitHub - danielalves96/claude-code-provider-gateway: The easiest way to use Claude Code with any LLM. Install the app, pick your provider, done.","url":"https://github.com/danielalves96/claude-code-provider-gateway"},{"title":"Openai-Claude-Deepseek-API-provider/en.md at main","url":"https://github.com/TechnologyStar/Openai-Claude-Deepseek-API-provider/blob/main/en.md"},{"title":"Microsoft AI Pricing Comparison: AI Builder vs API Call","url":"https://www.linkedin.com/posts/suhail-powerflow_here-are-2-pricing-screenshots-essentially-activity-7427630044212273152--c-0"},{"title":"Claude Instant API Pricing 2026 - Costs, Performance & Providers","url":"https://pricepertoken.com/pricing-page/model/anthropic-claude-instant"},{"title":"feat: Add Claude Code CLI as an AI Provider Option","url":"https://github.com/eyaltoledano/claude-task-master/issues/705"},{"title":"Feature Request: Add Claude (Anthropic) as LLM Provider","url":"https://github.com/icereed/paperless-gpt/issues/477"},{"title":"Support custom Claude provider model aliases","url":"https://github.com/coleam00/Archon/issues/1586"},{"title":"Enable Prompt Caching for Claude Code Provider (Persistent Session Architecture) · cline/cline · Discussion #9892","url":"https://github.com/cline/cline/discussions/9892"},{"title":"GitHub - ericc-ch/copilot-api: Turn GitHub Copilot into OpenAI/Anthropic API compatible server. Usable with Claude Code!","url":"https://github.com/ericc-ch/copilot-api"},{"title":"Intr